@startuml workflow_methodology
!theme vibrant
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #1976D2
skinparam ActivityFontSize 11
skinparam ArrowColor #424242
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam shadowing false

title JURI AI - Complete Workflow & Methodology

|#E8F5E9|User Actions|
start
:User uploads legal\ndocument (PDF/DOCX);
note right
  Supported formats:
  • PDF (max 10MB)
  • DOCX (max 10MB)
  • TXT (max 5MB)
end note

|#FFF9C4|Document Processing|
:Validate file type\nand scan for malware;

if (File valid and safe?) then (yes)
  :Extract text content;
  note right
    **Extraction Methods:**
    • PyMuPDF (primary)
    • PyPDF2 (fallback)
    • Tesseract OCR (scanned docs)
  end note
else (no)
  :Reject file with\nerror message;
  stop
endif

:Detect language;
note right
  Supported:
  • English
  • Hindi (future)
  • Marathi (future)
end note

if (Language supported?) then (yes)
else (no)
  :Return unsupported\nlanguage error;
  stop
endif

|#E3F2FD|Text Chunking|
:Segment text into\noverlapping chunks;
note right
  **Chunking Parameters:**
  • Size: 800 characters
  • Overlap: 100 chars (12.5%)
  • Separators: ¶, \n, ., ,
  
  **Preserves:**
  • Sentence boundaries
  • Legal section headers
  • Clause numbering
end note

:Generate metadata\nfor each chunk;
note right
  Metadata includes:
  • Document ID
  • Page number
  • Chunk index
  • Upload timestamp
  • User ID
end note

|#F3E5F5|Embedding Generation|
:Create vector embeddings\nusing Sentence-MPNET;
note right
  **Model:** all-mpnet-base-v2
  **Output:** 768-dim vectors
  **Normalization:** L2 norm
  **Batch size:** 32 chunks
end note

:Store vectors in\nPinecone database;
note right
  **Pinecone Config:**
  • Metric: Cosine similarity
  • Namespace: Per-user
  • Index type: Serverless
end note

|#FCE4EC|Query Processing|
partition "**User Query Flow**" {
  :User submits legal query\nvia chat interface;
  
  :Preprocess query;
  note right
    • Spell correction
    • Query expansion
    • Intent classification
  end note
  
  :Convert query to\n768-dim embedding;
  
  :Search Pinecone for\ntop-K similar chunks;
  note right
    **Retrieval:**
    • K = 5 chunks
    • Similarity threshold: 0.7
    • Filter by user/doc
  end note
  
  if (Relevant chunks found?) then (yes)
    :Rerank results using\nCross-Encoder;
    note right
      **Reranking:**
      • Model: ms-marco-MiniLM
      • Select top-3 chunks
      • Improves accuracy +6%
    end note
    
    :Construct augmented prompt\nwith context;
    note right
      **Prompt Structure:**
      1. System instructions
      2. Retrieved context
      3. User question
      4. Response format
      5. Citation requirements
    end note
    
    :Send to LLaMA 3.3 70B\nvia Groq API;
    note right
      **LLM Parameters:**
      • Temperature: 0.3
      • Max tokens: 1024
      • Top-p: 0.9
      • Frequency penalty: 0.2
    end note
    
    :Generate contextual answer\nwith source citations;
    
    :Post-process response;
    note right
      • Markdown formatting
      • Citation validation
      • Disclaimer injection
      • Toxicity filtering
    end note
    
  else (no)
    :Return "insufficient\ninformation" response;
  endif
  
  :Return answer to user;
}

|#FFF3E0|Contract Analysis|
partition "**Contract Review Flow**" {
  if (Document is a contract?) then (yes)
    :Extract contract clauses\nusing regex patterns;
    
    :Classify each clause\nusing Legal-BERT;
    note right
      **Classification:**
      • Model: Fine-tuned Legal-BERT
      • 15 clause types
      • Confidence threshold: 0.7
      • Accuracy: 84.76%
      
      **Clause Types:**
      • Confidentiality
      • Non-Compete
      • Termination
      • Liability
      • Payment Terms
      • IP Rights
      • ... (10 more)
    end note
    
    :Apply rule-based\nrisk detection;
    note right
      **Risk Validators:**
      • Non-compete duration
      • Jurisdiction alignment
      • Liability limits
      • Payment ambiguity
      • Termination fairness
      • ... (15+ more)
      
      **Indian Legal Compliance:**
      • Contract Act, 1872
      • Industrial Disputes Act
      • Labor laws
    end note
    
    :Calculate risk score\n(1-10 scale);
    note right
      **Risk Scoring:**
      • High severity: 10 points
      • Medium: 5 points
      • Low: 2 points
      • Normalized to 1-10
    end note
    
    :Compare with standard\ntemplate (if applicable);
    
    :Generate detailed\nanalysis report;
    note right
      **Report Contents:**
      • Identified clauses
      • Risk summary
      • Recommendations
      • Missing clauses
      • Compliance status
      • PDF export
    end note
    
    :Send report to user;
  else (no)
    :Skip contract analysis;
  endif
}

|#E0F2F1|Storage & Logging|
:Save chat history\nto MongoDB;

:Log user interaction\nfor analytics;

:Update document\nprocessing status;

:Send notification\n(if configured);

|#E8F5E9|User Response|
:Display answer/report\nin user interface;

if (User satisfied?) then (yes)
  :Mark as helpful;
  :Update model feedback;
else (no)
  :Collect feedback;
  :Flag for manual review;
endif

stop

legend right
  |= Color |= Component |
  |<#E8F5E9>| User Actions |
  |<#FFF9C4>| Document Processing |
  |<#E3F2FD>| Text Chunking |
  |<#F3E5F5>| Embedding |
  |<#FCE4EC>| Query Processing |
  |<#FFF3E0>| Contract Analysis |
  |<#E0F2F1>| Storage |
  
  **Performance Metrics:**
  • Avg query latency: 2.3s
  • RAG accuracy: 89%
  • Classification accuracy: 84.76%
  • Risk detection F1: 88.7%
end legend

@enduml
